window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She's 12. He's dead. But together they're going to save the world. Hopefully. </p> <p>The iconic first book in the best-selling Skulduggery Pleasant series. </p> <p>Stephanie's uncle Gordon is a writer of horror fiction. But when he dies and leaves her his estate, Stephanie learns that while he may have written horror it certainly wasn't fiction. Pursued by evil forces, Stephanie finds help from an unusual source - the wisecracking skeleton of a dead sorcerer.... </p>"; 
